3\. Introduction  
CrackTify is a desktop application that automatically detects wall cracks using image analysis and computer vision. Designed with a responsive interface, the app scales for mobile devices, allowing users to inspect walls on-site using their phone or review captured images on a desktop. This manual guides users through installation, operation, and troubleshooting for both platforms.
